-- India's Central Bank Says Monetary Policy Steps Needed to Cool Inflation
-- Kartik Goyal
-- 2010-07-26T11:32:21Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2010-07-26/india-s-central-bank-says-monetary-policy-steps-needed-to-cool-inflation.html

          
          
             India’s central bank said monetary
policy steps are a “necessity” to cool inflation, according to
a report on the economy released in Mumbai today. The bank is
scheduled to set its benchmark interest rates tomorrow.  
